INSERT INTO $DO_TDWH_SN_SYSTEM_EDW_STAGING_STG_DIM_BUNDLE ( BUNDLE_GROUP_ID,BUNDLE_PRODUCT_ID,BUNDLE_PRODUCT_NAME,META_CREATE_DATETIME,META_JOB_EXEC_ID) 
WITH  jnr_product_type 
AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_ORDER_LINE.GROUP_KEY AS BUNDLE_GROUP_ID
  FROM 
	$DO_TDWH_SN_LANDING_BENTO_PRODUCT_TYPE SRC_PRODUCT_TYPE 

 INNER JOIN
 $DO_TDWH_SN_LANDING_BENTO_ORDER_LINE SRC_ORDER_LINE 
ON
(SRC_ORDER_LINE.PRODUCT_TYPE_ID   = SRC_PRODUCT_TYPE.PRODUCT_TYPE_ID ) 

 INNER JOIN
 $DO_TDWH_SN_LANDING_BENTO_PRODUCT SRC_PRODUCT 
ON
(SRC_ORDER_LINE.PRODUCT_ID  = SRC_PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID ) 
WHERE 	SRC_PRODUCT_TYPE.LABEL = 'Bundle' AND SRC_ORDER_LINE.GROUP_KEY  <> '' AND SRC_ORDER_LINE.META_UPDATE_DATETIME  >= $MP_low_watermark_date  
) 
,SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.BUNDLE_GROUP_ID AS BUNDLE_GROUP_ID
 FROM 
	$DO_TDWH_SN_SYSTEM_ETL_EXCEPTION_STG_DIM_BUNDLE SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE  
 WHERE 
	SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.META_JOB_EXEC_ID = $MP_prev_job_exec_id  
) 
, uni_bundle_base AS 
( 
	SELECT 
	jnr_product_type.BUNDLE_GROUP_ID AS BUNDLE_GROUP_ID
	FROM 
		jnr_product_type 

Union 
	SELECT 
	SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.BUNDLE_GROUP_ID AS BUNDLE_GROUP_ID
 	FROM 
		SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE 
 ) 
,  jnr_bundle_base 
AS 
( 
SELECT 
	row_number() over(partition by SRC_ORDER_LINE_1.GROUP_KEY ,SRC_ORDER_LINE_1.PRODUCT_ID ,SRC_PRODUCT_1.LABEL order by SRC_ORDER_LINE_1.GROUP_KEY ,SRC_ORDER_LINE_1.PRODUCT_ID ,SRC_PRODUCT_1.LABEL) AS row_num
	,SRC_ORDER_LINE_1.GROUP_KEY AS BUNDLE_GROUP_ID
	,SRC_ORDER_LINE_1.PRODUCT_ID AS bundle_product_id
	,SRC_PRODUCT_1.LABEL AS bundle_product_name
  FROM 
	uni_bundle_base 

 INNER JOIN
 $DO_TDWH_SN_LANDING_BENTO_ORDER_LINE SRC_ORDER_LINE_1 
ON
(uni_bundle_base.BUNDLE_GROUP_ID  = SRC_ORDER_LINE_1.GROUP_KEY ) 

 INNER JOIN
 $DO_TDWH_SN_LANDING_BENTO_PRODUCT_TYPE SRC_PRODUCT_TYPE_1 
ON
(SRC_ORDER_LINE_1.PRODUCT_TYPE_ID = SRC_PRODUCT_TYPE_1.PRODUCT_TYPE_ID) 

 INNER JOIN
 $DO_TDWH_SN_LANDING_BENTO_PRODUCT SRC_PRODUCT_1 
ON
(SRC_ORDER_LINE_1.PRODUCT_ID  = SRC_PRODUCT_1.PRODUCT_ID ) 
WHERE 	SRC_PRODUCT_TYPE_1.LABEL = 'Bundle' 
) 
,  expr_meta_attributes 
 AS 
( 
SELECT 
	jnr_bundle_base.BUNDLE_GROUP_ID AS BUNDLE_GROUP_ID
	,jnr_bundle_base.bundle_product_id AS bundle_product_id
	,jnr_bundle_base.bundle_product_name AS bundle_product_name
	,$MP_meta_datetime AS meta_create_datetime
	,$$AuditId  AS meta_job_exec_id
 FROM 
	jnr_bundle_base

WHERE jnr_bundle_base.row_num = 1 
),TGT_STG_DIM_BUNDLE 
AS 
( 
SELECT 
	expr_meta_attributes.BUNDLE_GROUP_ID BUNDLE_GROUP_ID
	,expr_meta_attributes.bundle_product_id bundle_product_id
	,expr_meta_attributes.bundle_product_name bundle_product_name
	,expr_meta_attributes.meta_create_datetime meta_create_datetime
	,expr_meta_attributes.meta_job_exec_id meta_job_exec_id
 FROM 
	expr_meta_attributes 
)  
SELECT 
	TGT_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.BUNDLE_GROUP_ID AS BUNDLE_GROUP_ID
	,TGT_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.bundle_product_id AS bundle_product_id
	,TGT_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.bundle_product_name AS bundle_product_name
	,TGT_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.meta_create_datetime AS meta_create_datetime
	,TGT_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.meta_job_exec_id AS meta_job_exec_id
 FROM 
	TGT_STG_DIM_BUNDLE

CREATE TABLE $TFORM_JNR_dim_bundle AS 
(  
WITH SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.ID AS ID
	,SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.BUNDLE_GROUP_ID AS BUNDLE_GROUP_ID
	,SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.BUNDLE_PRODUCT_ID AS BUNDLE_PRODUCT_ID
	,SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.BUNDLE_PRODUCT_NAME AS BUNDLE_PRODUCT_NAME
	,SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.META_CREATE_DATETIME AS META_CREATE_DATETIME
	,$SP_hash_expr.T1H AS meta_row_hash_type1
	,$SP_hash_expr.T2H AS meta_row_hash_type2
 FROM 
	$DO_TDWH_SN_SYSTEM_EDW_STAGING_STG_DIM_BUNDLE SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE  
) 
,SRC_DIM_BUNDLE  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_DIM_BUNDLE.BUNDLE_KEY AS BUNDLE_KEY
	,SRC_DIM_BUNDLE.BUNDLE_GROUP_ID AS BUNDLE_GROUP_ID
	,$SP_hash_expr.T1H AS meta_row_hash_type1
	,$SP_hash_expr.T2H AS meta_row_hash_type2
 FROM 
	$DO_TDWH_SN_EDW_MART_DIM_BUNDLE SRC_DIM_BUNDLE  
 WHERE 
	SRC_DIM_BUNDLE.META_IS_CURRENT = 1 
) 
,SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE_EXCP  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE_EXCP.ID AS ID
 FROM 
	$DO_TDWH_SN_SYSTEM_ETL_EXCEPTION_STG_DIM_BUNDLE SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE_EXCP  
 WHERE 
	NVL(UPPER(SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE_EXCP.META_ROW_EXCEPTION_TYPE), '') like '%ERROR%' AND SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE_EXCP.META_JOB_EXEC_ID = $$AuditId  
) 
SELECT 
	SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.BUNDLE_GROUP_ID AS BUNDLE_GROUP_ID
	,SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.BUNDLE_PRODUCT_ID AS BUNDLE_PRODUCT_ID
	,SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.BUNDLE_PRODUCT_NAME AS BUNDLE_PRODUCT_NAME
	,SRC_DIM_BUNDLE.BUNDLE_KEY AS BUNDLE_KEY
	,$$AuditId  AS job_exec_id
	,CASE 
WHEN SRC_DIM_BUNDLE.BUNDLE_GROUP_ID   IS NULL THEN 'INS'
WHEN SRC_DIM_BUNDLE.meta_row_hash_type2   <> SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.meta_row_hash_type2   THEN 'TY2'
WHEN SRC_DIM_BUNDLE.meta_row_hash_type1   <> SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.meta_row_hash_type1   THEN 'TY1'
END AS operation_ind
	,SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.META_CREATE_DATETIME  AS meta_timestamp
	,to_timestamp_ntz('9999-12-31 00:00:00') AS meta_end_timestamp_ins
	,CASE WHEN CASE 
WHEN SRC_DIM_BUNDLE.BUNDLE_GROUP_ID   IS NULL THEN 'INS'
WHEN SRC_DIM_BUNDLE.meta_row_hash_type2   <> SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.meta_row_hash_type2   THEN 'TY2'
WHEN SRC_DIM_BUNDLE.meta_row_hash_type1   <> SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.meta_row_hash_type1   THEN 'TY1'
END  = 'INS' THEN to_timestamp_ntz('1900-01-01 00:00:00') ELSE SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.META_CREATE_DATETIME  END AS meta_effective_start_timestamp_ins
	,1 AS current_ind_ins
	,dateadd(second, -1, SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.META_CREATE_DATETIME) AS meta_end_timestamp_ty2_upd
	,0 AS current_ind_typ2_upd
  FROM 
	SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE 

 LEFT OUTER JOIN
 SRC_DIM_BUNDLE 
ON
(SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.BUNDLE_GROUP_ID = SRC_DIM_BUNDLE.BUNDLE_GROUP_ID ) 

 LEFT OUTER JOIN
 SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE_EXCP 
ON
(SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.ID = SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE_EXCP.ID ) 
WHERE 	SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE_EXCP.ID is NULL 
 
)

	,1 AS current_ind_ins
	,dateadd(second, -1, SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE.META_CREATE_DATETIME) AS meta_end_timestamp_ty2_upd
	,0 AS current_ind_typ2_upd
  FROM 
	SRC_STG_DIM_BUNDLE 

 LEFT OUTER JOIN
 SRC_DIM_BUNDLE 
ON
